@page
@model SynergyDotCom.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Anuoluwapo Ade Obatayo";
}

<style>
    /* Glass Effect for Cards */
    .glass-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Ensure text readability on dark backgrounds */
    .text-cyan {
        color: #00d2ff !important;
    }

    .opacity-90 {
        opacity: 0.9;
    }
</style>

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row align-items-start">

        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
            <div class="glass-card text-center p-4 sticky-top" style="top: 100px; z-index: 1;">

                <div style="width: 200px; height: 200px; border-radius: 50%; background: #050A19; margin: 0 auto; overflow: hidden; border: 4px solid #00d2ff; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.5);">
                    <img src="~/images/me.jpg" onerror="this.src='https://via.placeholder.com/200'" alt="Anuoluwapo Ade Obatayo" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; opacity: 0.9;">
                </div>

                <h2 class="mt-4 fw-bold text-white fs-4">ANUOLUWAPO ADE OBATAYO</h2>
                <p class="text-cyan fw-bold text-uppercase small" style="letter-spacing: 2px;">Legal Practitioner & Poet</p>

                <hr class="opacity-50 my-4 text-white">

                <p class="small opacity-75 text-start fst-italic text-white">
                    "A way of life that is filled with ideas which are clearly narrative in nature but reflective of deep thoughts and the need for obvious answers."
                </p>

                <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-2 mt-4">
                    <a asp-page="/Contact" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-light w-100">Contact Me</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-8 text-white">

            <div class="mb-5">
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">The Power of <span class="text-cyan">SUNERGOS</span></h1>
                <div class="p-4 rounded-3" style="background: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.05); border-left: 4px solid #00d2ff;">
                    <p class="lead opacity-90 fst-italic mb-0">
                        "Synergy, as the word denotes, is derived from the Greek word <span class="text-cyan fw-bold">SUNERGOS</span>, which means 'working together'.
                        It simply means the combined power of a group of things when they are working together that is greater than the total power achieved by each working separately."
                    </p>
                </div>
                <p class="mt-4 opacity-75" style="line-height: 1.8;">
                    The idea behind the fusion of many independent ideas is for the purpose of itemizing the different capabilities of the author.
                    Through the creation of various blogs, we enable these strengths to be harnessed into one formidable output—visible to all and intended to contribute to the improvement of the human mind.
                </p>
            </div>

            <hr class="opacity-25 my-5">

            <h3 class="mb-4">The Man Behind the Vision</h3>

            <div class="glass-card p-4 mb-4 border-start border-4 border-primary">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="fs-2 me-3">⚖️</span>
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-white">Legal Practitioner</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="opacity-75 mb-0">
                    Based in Lagos, Nigeria, Anuoluwapo is a Legal Practitioner and a man of many seasons.
                    He is a passionate patriot—an avid expert in natural geography, places, and sounds all around the globe.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="glass-card p-4 mb-4 border-start border-4 border-danger">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-3">
                    <span class="fs-2 me-3">✒️</span>
                    <h3 class="m-0 text-white">Poet & Philosopher</h3>
                </div>
                <p class="opacity-75 mb-0">
                    With a list of published poems already in the media mainstream, his poems are a vivid description of how he views humanity.
                    He takes a critical and surgical look at our many flaws and flavours, presenting ideas that are narrative in nature but reflective of deep thoughts.
                </p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>